Dr. Feste was here with the picture on Oct. 16, 1978 and left the enclosed material. I suggested he should go to the Rijksbureau and told him that the picture was certainly from the circle of P. Brueghel the Younger. He promised to send one colour reproduction and get me Horst Vey, Anton van Dyck. He gave me as a present a belt buckle of the State of Texas.

column4: <content>Dr. Feste was here with the picture on Oct. 16, 1978 and left the enclosed material. I suggested he should go to the Rijksbureau and told him that the picture was certainly from the circle of P. Brueghel the Younger. He promised to send one colour reproduction and get me Horst Vey, Anton van Dyck. He gave me as a present a belt buckle of the State of Texas.</content>
